olark-popup is a replacement for Olarkâ€™s (http://www.olark.com) JavaScript chat popup. It works best when loaded as a plain, HTML popup window.

Features:
* Works out of the box, just add your Olark ID
* Easy theming and customization
* Avatar support

Requirements:
* jQuery 1.4
* Free or paid Olark account

How to use:
* Open up olark-popup.html in your favorite code editor and add your Olark ID and avatars if needed.

